{"tid":1603587,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"[戰略post] 一個和理非都可以勝任又十分重要的職業","createTime":"2019-09-29T17:07:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T09:56:57.000Z","uid":313697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4bf231c61a0bd922bb003afa9a7e70cd925ca3fd","tid":1603587,"uid":313697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:07:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">就係哨兵！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n好多手足都認為哨兵只存在於前線同撤退，其實早期預警都係一個十分重要的部分。只要提早知道啲狗的位置，如防暴、狗車等等， 都有助前線手足進場。就好似今日sogo的情況，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">早期預警可以協助有裝的手足迴避。</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而早期預警需要的是密度和準確度， 因此十分適合不想有被捕風險的和理非係街坊look嘅情況下行動。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個職業的法律責任竟然是<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">零！！</span></span><br />\n喺街度見到咁多狗隻當然要放上網打下卡啦，香港有冇肖像權，簡直係任影唔嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唯一可能要犧牲嘅<br />\n可能就係手足要早起床少咗啲瞓覺時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n下次發夢毫無意外就係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">六區開花</span></span>，狗狗同黨鐵毫無意外 應該都會好似927一樣再次合作，早早妨礙大家出門。<br />\n因此正如上面所講，有裝的手足可能需要早出門，因此早期預警必須更早開始，如早上八時開始發動， 才能發揮最大的作用，協助手足迴避和到達該地區。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家可以使用<a href=\"http://hkmap.live\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkmap.live&d=WosQ6lw2L4bsKafLDhDjrawVmkNCIo3TbJkxuaymrXU%3D&h=bb08aa1c\" target=\"_blank\">hkmap.live</a><br />\n認證了之後開始報料，讓手足可以實時 知道情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">十月一日 賀佢老母</span></span>"},{"pid":"84517ad855f25289558a39e95a973e83b83b5c7d","tid":1603587,"uid":313697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:09:31.000Z","msg":"自膠開錯台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48dc8caa62b221b341b2b0182de89a309f2e6438","tid":1603587,"uid":313697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T09:56:57.000Z","msg":"推"}]}